Java String toCharArray() Method

[Java String toCharArray() method](https://www.flowerbrackets.com/java-string-tochararray-method/)

Java String toCharArray() method converts given string into new character array.

Letâ€™s see tochararray java method example or string tochararray java.

public class StringToCharArrayDemo
{
   public static void main(String[] args)
   {
      String strInput = new String("HelloWorld");
      // using toCharArray() method java
      char[] chArray = strInput.toCharArray();
      System.out.println("Character array: ");
      for(char ch : chArray)
      {
         System.out.println(ch);
      }
   }
}


Output:

Character array:
H
e
l
l
o
W
o
r
l
d
